26 A.C.A 19-5-601 and 19-5-602 within forty-five (45) days.
27 Any carry forward of unexpended balance of funding as authorized herein,
28 may be carried forward under the following conditions:
29 (1) Prior to June 30, 2025 2026 the Agency shall by written statement
30 set forth its reason(s) for the need to carry forward said funding to the
31 Department of Finance and Administration Office of Budget;
32 (2) The Department of Finance and Administration Office of Budget shall
33 report to the Arkansas Legislative Council all amounts carried forward by the
34 September Arkansas Legislative Council or Joint Budget Committee meeting
35 which report shall include the name of the Agency, Board, Commission or
36 Institution and the amount of the funding carried forward, the program name
